data.eml:eml: New Dicerurini from Europe, mostly Sweden (Diptera: Cecidomyiidae, Porricondylinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jaschhof, Mathias, Jaschhof, Catrin (2019): New Dicerurini from Europe, mostly Sweden (Diptera: Cecidomyiidae, Porricondylinae). Zootaxa 4559 (2): 245-264, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4559.2.2
